title: For Sale:  9MM AR-15 (will sell as complete firearm or upper only)
postcontent:
I have for sale a complete AR-15 9mm Pistol.  I had this listed as just an upper previously, but now am selling as a complete ready to shoot pistol.

It includes a JP free float tube, Magpul Angled Fore Grip (AFG), Magpul flip up BUIS, Magpul ASAP single point sling mount and sling, and pistol buffer tube.  It comes with 2 mags.

Lower is PSA, Upper is DPMS.  It is a standard AR-Lower that will function just as any other with any AR upper.  Just turn a screw to remove the 9mm mag block (metal), slap another upper on it, and you are GTG.  It will accept a standard stock and buffer tube as well.  

This is a proven set up that I used to run on a registered full auto lower, but it was NOT abused.  

The ProPoint scope is NOT included (I just didn't want to unmount and lose zero), though I will throw it in for another $50.  

It uses the standard Colt Blowback system and UZI type mags.  The magwell block is secured into the lower from the bottom.

Feel free to ask any questions by email or phone.  REDACTED
